    "questionText": "The correct match between Item-I (starting\nmaterial) and Item-II (reagent) for the\npreparation of benzaldehyde is :\n<br><br><style type=\"text/css\">\n.tg  {border-collapse:collapse;border-spacing:0;}\n.tg td{border-color:black;border-style:solid;border-width:1px;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;font-size:14px;\n  overflow:hidden;padding:10px 5px;word-break:normal;}\n.tg th{border-color:black;border-style:solid;border-width:1px;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;font-size:14px;\n  font-weight:normal;overflow:hidden;padding:10px 5px;word-break:normal;}\n.tg .tg-baqh{text-align:center;vertical-align:top}\n</style>\n<table class=\"tg\">\n<thead>\n  <tr>\n    <th class=\"tg-baqh\"><b>Item-I</b></th>\n    <th class=\"tg-baqh\"><b>Item-II</b></th>\n  </tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n  <tr>\n    <td class=\"tg-baqh\">(I) Benzene</td>\n    <td class=\"tg-baqh\">(P) HCl and SnCl<sub>2</sub>,\nH<sub>3</sub>O<sup>+</sup></td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n    <td class=\"tg-baqh\">(II) Benzonitrile</td>\n    <td class=\"tg-baqh\">(Q) H<sub>2</sub>, Pd-BaSO<sub>4</sub>, S\nand quinoline</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n    <td class=\"tg-baqh\">(III) Benzoyl Chloride</td>\n    <td class=\"tg-baqh\">(R) CO, HCl and AlCl<sub>3</sub></td>\n  </tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>",
    "options": [
      "(I) - (R), (II) - (P) and (III) - (Q)",
